======================================================================
PART 2: REPUNIT AND CYCLOTOMIC STRUCTURE
======================================================================

  Forbidden values and their representations:
    7 = R₃(2) = Φ₃(2) = 2²+2+1 = 111₂
    21 = R₃(4) = Φ₃(4) = 4²+4+1 = 111₄ = 3×7
    63 = R₆(2) = 2⁶-1 = 111111₂ = 333₄ = 9×7
    189 = 7×27 = 7×3³ — ACHIEVABLE at n=7!

  WHY 189 survives:
    189 in binary: 10111101
    189 in base 4: 2331₄

  The key: 63 = 333₄ (repdigit in base 4), but 189 = 2331₄ (NOT repdigit)
  The repdigit/repunit connection is the obstruction, not just 7×3^k!

  Repdigits in base 4:
    1₄ = 1
    11₄ = 5
    111₄ = 21 — FORBIDDEN at n=6
